description	"Jedi Healer:
A Jedi who can Heal and Re-energize allies.

^2Weaponry:
- Dual Lightsabers
-- Dual / Yellow Styles
-- Saber / Blaster Defense 1
-- 10% Less DMG
- 1 Sonic Detonator

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (2)
- Pull  (2)
- Sense (3)
- Team Heal (1)
- Team Energize (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Resistant to Melee Attacks
- View Ally Stats
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Falling
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Focus (1)
- 1 Extra Life

^3Abilities:
- Health Dispenser [Hold Use to Heal Allies]
- Ammo Dispenser"